channel.title: RuneTopList Voting
channel.description: First off, I don't know if this is the wrong section for this or not, so please, if it is, do not hammer me with comments such as "Wrong section," or "god noob get a life and learn the sections," ect ect.. I have set up the runeTopList Voting script, but I have come across a problem. The script makes you put in the website callback for runetoplist, but considering that website is not online anymore, it is impossible. I know there is a way to take off this requirement, I just don't know how. If anyone could share their knowledge with me that would be excellent, because as of now, whenever my players vote on all of the links, it says "Please vote on all links." Thanks for any help in advance. :confused:
